#{\footnote winchng}${\footnote Changes from earlier versions}K{\footnote Nonogram solver v2.0 for Windows;Changes from earlier versions}
{\f4\fs30\b Changes from earlier versions}
\plain \f4\fs20
\par
\par
Version 2.0 of the Nonogram Solver for Windows is a significant new release. It provides improved solve times of up to 33% faster. It also uses Borland's custom controls to provide an improved user interface and corrects a number of small bugs. However, most bugs were corrected in v1.1 and v1.1a. The speed improvement has been obtained by optimising the \plain \uldb\f4\fs20 
Combinational\plain \uldb\v\f4\fs20 combin\plain \f4\fs20  algorithm. Also, see the section on \plain \uldb\f4\fs20 VARS\plain \uldb\v\f4\fs20 vars\plain \f4\fs20  for more information. \par
\par\b\f4\fs24
Also See
\par\plain \uldb\f4\fs20
Contents\plain \uldb\v\f4\fs20 main_contents\plain \uldb\f4\fs20 \par
